#eNCA's Dasen Thathiah has more details. Courtesy #DStv403 DURBAN - Search teams and families are refusing to give up on missing persons in KwaZulu-Natal. Over 50 people are still unaccounted for. READ: Search continues for KZN flood victims The Gumbi family in Kwangcolosi in the eThekwini municipality has taken their quest to find loved ones, to the Inanda Dam. They want help to find their three little daughters. eNCA reporter Dasen Thathiah is in the water with them and provides an update.